articles.author: Reis Thebault
articles.title: After I-10 closure, America's car capital grapples with freeway future - The Washington Post
articles.description: After an earthquake closed the freeway in 1994, the reaction was to rebuild. This time, calls are rising to rethink the region’s car-centric approach.
